Waarp Common Digest package
org.waarp.common.digest Classes implementing digests support (MD2, MD5, SHA1, SHA-256/384/512, CRC32, ADLER32)

MD5 can be implemented through Fast MD5 implementation, but can be reverted to JVM native digest also.

 

The Waarp Digest project contains several classes that are common with different sub projects of Waarp (FTP, R66, ...). These classes are for Digest implementation.
